Synopsis:

The second volume of the book of "Saiyuki Reload Blast" is finally released! The limited edition is a mini -drama CD of the original script written by Kazuya Minekura based on the short manga recorded in Volume 1 of "Saiyuki Reload Blast". Attached !!
